                englishText: "The Messenger of Allāh (ﷺ) said: \"Truly excellent is the situation of a believer! Everything is to his advantage and this is enjoyed by none except him. When he experiences happiness, he is grateful and it is to his advantage. When he experiences distress, he is patient and it is to his advantage.\" (Muslim)",
