                englishText: "The Messenger of Allāh (ﷺ) said: \"The world is sweet and green. Allāh has granted you authority over it and He then sees how you act. Beware of the world and beware of women. The first test and tribulation of the Banī Isrā'īl was regarding women.\" (Muslim)",
