                englishText: "The Messenger of Allāh (ﷺ) said: \"All of my Ummah shall enter Paradise except those who reject.\" He was asked: \"O Messenger of Allāh! Who are those who reject?\" He replied: \"Those who obey me shall enter Paradise and those who disobey me reject.\" (Bukhārī)",
