                englishText: "The Messenger of Allāh (ﷺ) said: \"No person is murdered unjustly without a share of that blood being placed on the first son of Ādam (عليه السلام) because he was the first to initiate the act of murder.\" (Bukhārī, Muslim)",
                grade: "Sahih",
