                englishText: "The Messenger of Allāh (ﷺ) said: \"Abstain from oppression because oppression will be a cause of intense darkness on the day of Qiyāmah. Abstain from miserliness because it destroyed those before you. It prompted them to shed blood and to consider as lawful all that was made unlawful to them.\" (Muslim)",
