                englishText: "The Messenger of Allāh (ﷺ) said: \"Help your brother irrespective of whether he is the oppressor or the oppressed.\" A man asked: \"O Messenger of Allāh! I can help him if he is oppressed, but how can I help him if he is an oppressor?\" He replied: \"You should stop him or prevent him from oppression. This is how you should help him.\" (Bukhārī)",
