                englishText: "The Messenger of Allāh (ﷺ) said: \"The worst type of food is that of walīmah in which those who need to attend are prevented from joining in and those who refuse to attend are invited to it. One who does not accept an invitation has disobeyed Allāh and His Messenger (ﷺ).\" A narration of Bukhārī and Muslim has: \"That feast of walīmah is evil in which the rich are invited while the poor are left out.\" (Muslim)",
