                englishText: "A poor woman carrying her two daughters came begging to me and I gave her three dates to eat. She gave one date to each of them and raised the third date to her mouth to eat it. But, her two daughters asked her to feed it to them. So she split the date which she wanted to eat between them. I was surprised by her conduct and told the Messenger of Allāh (ﷺ) about it. He said: \"Allāh made Paradise obligatory upon her by virtue of her action, or freed her from the Hell-fire because of it.\" (Muslim)",
