                englishText: "I asked: \"O Messenger of Allāh! What right does a wife have over the husband?\" He replied: \"That you feed her when you eat, you clothe her when you clothe yourself, you do not strike at her face, you do not abuse her and you do not sever relations with her except at home.\" (Abū Dāwūd)",
                grade: "Hasan",
