                englishText: "The Messenger of Allāh (ﷺ) said: \"Each one of you is a shepherd and each one of you is answerable for his flock. A leader is a shepherd. A man is a shepherd over his family. A woman is a shepherd over her husband's house and his children. All of you are shepherds and each of you is responsible for his flock.\" (Bukhārī, Muslim)",
