                englishText: "A man asked: \"O Messenger of Allāh! Tell me of an action that will enter me into Paradise and keep me away from the Hell-fire.\" The Messenger of Allāh (ﷺ) said: \"Worship Allāh, do not ascribe any partners to Him, establish ṣalāh, give zakāh and maintain ties of kinship.\" (Bukhārī, Muslim)",
                grade: "Sahih",
