                englishText: "I set out on a journey with Jarīr ibn 'Abdullāh al-Bajalī (رضي الله عنه) and he attended to my needs, so I said to him: 'Do not do so.' He said: 'I saw the Anṣār doing so for the Messenger of Allāh (ﷺ) and I took an oath that if I accompanied any of them, I would serve them (and you are from them).'\" (Bukhārī, Muslim)",
