                englishText: "The Messenger of Allāh (ﷺ) said regarding the Anṣār: \"None but a believer loves them and none but a hypocrite hates them. Allāh (ﷻ) loves one who loves them and Allāh (ﷻ) hates one who hates them.\" (Bukhārī, Muslim)",
