                englishText: "I heard the Messenger of Allāh (ﷺ) saying: \"The person who will be meted out the lightest punishment amongst the people of the Hell-fire will be one who will have two embers placed in the hollows of his feet which will cause his brains to boil. He will not consider anyone to be suffering more than him, yet he will be meted out the lightest punishment of all.\" (Bukhārī, Muslim)",
                grade: "Sahih",
