                englishText: "The Messenger of Allāh (ﷺ) said: \"On the day of Qiyāmah people will perspire to such an extent that their perspiration will seep into the ground as deep as seventy cubits and it will bridle them until it reaches their ears.\" (Bukhārī, Muslim)",
