                englishText: "The Messenger of Allāh (ﷺ) said: \"The feet of a person will not move (on the day of Qiyāmah) until he is asked about his life and how he spent it, about his knowledge and how he utilized it, about his wealth and from where he acquired it and where he spent it and about his body and how he wore it out.\" (Tirmidhī)",
