                englishText: "A man said to the Messenger of Allāh (ﷺ): \"O Messenger of Allāh! I love you.\" He said: \"Think carefully about what you are saying.\" The man said: \"By Allāh, I love you,\" three times. The Messenger of Allāh (ﷺ) said: \"If you really love me, prepare yourself with the shield of poverty because poverty comes more swiftly to the one who loves me than flood water to its destination.\" (Tirmidhī)",
