                englishText: "The Messenger of Allāh (ﷺ) slept on a straw mat and when he stood up, it would leave marks on the side of his body. We said: 'O Messenger of Allāh! We could get a mattress for you.' He said: 'What have I to do with this world? I am merely like a rider in this world who takes shade beneath a tree and then proceeds, leaving it behind.'\" (Tirmidhī)",
