                englishText: "The Messenger of Allāh (ﷺ) said: \"I stood at the door of Paradise and noticed that the majority who entered it were the destitute, while the wealthy were held back. However, the inmates of the Hell-fire had already been sent off to the Hell-fire.\" (Bukhārī, Muslim)",
