                englishText: "I came to the Messenger of Allāh (ﷺ) and he said: 'Have you come to ask about righteousness?' I replied: 'Yes.' He said: 'Ask your heart. Righteousness is that with which the soul is at peace and the heart is at peace; and sin is that which creates doubt in the heart and causes hesitation in the chest, even if people give you a verdict, even if people give you a verdict.'\" (Aḥmad, al-Dārimī)",
