                englishText: "I heard the Messenger of Allāh (ﷺ) saying in this very house of mine: \"O Allāh! Whoever is appointed over the affairs of my Ummah and he inconveniences them, then You inconvenience him; and whoever is appointed over the affairs of my Ummah and he is kind to them, then You be kind to him.\" (Muslim)",
