                englishText: "He went to 'Ubaydullāh ibn Ziyād and said to him: \"O my son! I heard the Messenger of Allāh (ﷺ) saying: 'The worst of rulers are those who are harsh upon their subjects.' So be careful that you are not from amongst them.\" (Muslim)",
