                englishText: "A man came to the Messenger of Allāh (ﷺ) and said: 'O Messenger of Allāh! I intend going on a journey so give me provisions.' He said: 'May Allāh provide you with righteousness.' The man said: 'Give me more.' He said: 'May He forgive your sins.' The man said: 'Give me more.' He said: 'May He make goodness easy for you wherever you are.'\" (Tirmidhī)",
