                englishText: "Milk which had been mixed with water was brought to the Messenger of Allāh (ﷺ). A Bedouin was sitting to his right and Abū Bakr (رضي الله عنه) to his left. He (ﷺ) drank some and then gave it to the Bedouin, saying: \"The one to the right, and then the one to his right.\" (Bukhārī, Muslim)",
