                englishText: "It was time for ṣalāh and those who lived nearby went to their houses, while the others remained behind. A bowl which was made of rock was brought to the Messenger of Allāh (ﷺ). It was so small that he could not even extend his palm in it, however, all present performed wuḍū' in it.\" People asked (Anas رضي الله عنه): \"How many were you?\" He replied: \"More than 80.\" (Bukhārī, Muslim)",
