                commentary: `As mentioned previously, this was a green striped garment, and not completely green in colour. A similar narration of Ya'lā ibn Umayyah (رضي الله عنه) states that he saw the Messenger of Allāh (ﷺ) performing ṭawāf of the Ka'bah whilst wearing a green-striped upper garment, with the right side over the right shoulder. (Abū Dāwūd)`
