                englishText: "The Messenger of Allāh (ﷺ) permitted al-Zubayr and 'Abd al-Raḥmān ibn 'Awf (رضي الله عنهما) to wear silk because of an itch they were suffering from.\" (Bukhārī, Muslim)",
