                englishText: "Abū al-Malīḥ narrates from his father (رضي الله عنه) that the Messenger of Allāh (ﷺ) prohibited using the skins of animals of prey. (Abū Dāwūd, Tirmidhī) A narration of Imām Tirmidhī states: \"He prohibited sitting on skins of animals of prey.\"",
