                englishText: "The Messenger of Allāh (ﷺ) said: \"One who sits in a place without remembering Allāh (ﷻ) therein, is subjected to a shortcoming from Allāh (ﷻ), and one who lies down in a place without remembering Allāh (ﷻ) therein, is subjected to a shortcoming from Allāh (ﷻ).\" (Abū Dāwūd)",
