                englishText: "The Messenger of Allāh (ﷺ) said: \"None of you should make a person get up from his seat and then take his place, but you should be accommodating and make place.\" If anyone stood up from his place to allow Ibn 'Umar (رضي الله عنه) to sit, he would not sit in it. (Bukhārī, Muslim)",
