                englishText: "The Messenger of Allāh (ﷺ) said: \"Whoever sits in any place without remembering Allāh (ﷻ) therein, will suffer a shortcoming from Allāh (ﷻ). Whoever lies down in a place without remembering Allāh (ﷻ) therein, will suffer a shortcoming from Allāh (ﷻ).\" (Abū Dāwūd)",
