                englishText: "The Messenger of Allāh (ﷺ) said: \"A Muslim has five rights over another Muslim: to reply to the salām, visit the ill, attend funerals, accept an invitation, and say yarḥamukallāh to the one who sneezes.\" (Bukhārī, Muslim)",
