                englishText: "He complained to the Messenger of Allāh (ﷺ) of a pain which he was experiencing in his body. The Messenger of Allāh (ﷺ) said to him: \"Place your hand on the portion of your body where you are experiencing pain and say, 'In the name of Allāh,' three times. Then say, 'I seek refuge in the power and might of Allāh from the evil of that which I experience and fear,' seven times.\" (Muslim)",
