                englishText: "The Messenger of Allāh (ﷺ) said: \"He who visits an ill person whose time of death has not yet come and says seven times in his presence, 'I ask Allāh the great, the Lord of the grand Throne, to cure you,' Allāh will cure him from that illness.\" (Abū Dāwūd, Tirmidhī)",
