                englishText: "Jibrā'īl (عليه السلام) came to the Messenger of Allāh (ﷺ) and asked: \"O Muḥammad, are you complaining (of any illness)?\" He replied: \"Yes.\" He said: \"In the name of Allāh, I make an incantation for you from everything that may harm you, from the evil of every soul or envious eye. May Allāh cure you. In the name of Allāh, I make an incantation for you.\" (Muslim)",
