                englishText: "I saw the Messenger of Allāh (ﷺ) while he was in the throes of death and with him was a bowl of water. He would insert his hand in the bowl and wipe his face with the water. He would then say: \"O Allāh, help me in the pains and pangs of death.\" (Tirmidhī)",
                grade: "Hasan",
