                englishText: "I heard the Messenger of Allāh (ﷺ) saying: \"If there are three people in a village or desert region and the congregational ṣalāh is not established between them, then Shaiṭān most certainly overpowers them. You must therefore adhere to the Muslim congregation because a wolf devours the sheep that strays.\" (Abū Dāwūd, Nasā'ī)",
