                englishText: "The Messenger of Allāh (ﷺ) used to walk between the rows from one end to the other, passing his hand over our chests and shoulders, and saying: \"Do not stand unevenly or your hearts will become disunited.\" He used to say: \"Allāh and His angels send salutations to the front rows.\" (Abū Dāwūd, Aḥmad, Ḥākim)",
