                englishText: "Abū Hurayrah (رضي الله عنه) and Ibn 'Umar (رضي الله عنهما) narrate that they heard the Messenger of Allāh (ﷺ) say, while sitting on his pulpit: \"People should stop abandoning the Jumu'ah ṣalāh or else Allāh will seal their hearts and they will definitely be included among the heedless.\" (Muslim, Ibn Mājah, Nasā'ī)",
