                commentary: `This ḥadīth was mentioned previously. See ḥadīth 182. It is repeated here to show the importance of zakāh. Scholars state that ṣalāh and zakāh have been mentioned as they are the most important physical and monetary acts of worship, however, all the injunctions of Islām are applicable.`
