                commentary: `One is prohibited from fasting one or two days before Ramaḍān as this will outwardly seem that one is adding to the fasts of Ramaḍān. However, if one is in the habit of fasting on that day, namely a Monday and Thursday, or every alternate day, then there is no harm in fasting.`
