                englishText: "The Messenger of Allāh (ﷺ) used to break the fast with fresh dates before performing ṣalāh. If there were no fresh dates, then with dry dates. If there were no dry dates, then he would take a few sips of water.\" (Abū Dāwūd, Tirmidhī)",
