                englishText: "I asked: 'O Messenger of Allāh! Tell me about wuḍū'.' He said: 'Perform wuḍū' thoroughly, pass water between the fingers, and place water into the nose thoroughly, unless you are fasting.'\" (Abū Dāwūd, Tirmidhī, Ibn Mājah, Bayhaqī)",
