                englishText: "Mu'ādhah al-'Adawiyyah narrates that she asked 'Ā'ishah (رضي الله عنها): \"Did the Messenger of Allāh (ﷺ) keep fast for three days every month?\" She replied: \"Yes.\" I asked: \"Which part of the month did he fast?\" She replied: \"He did not fast any specific days of the month.\" (Muslim, Abū Dāwūd, Ibn Mājah)",
