                englishText: "The Messenger of Allāh (ﷺ) was asked: \"Which is the best of actions?\" He replied: \"Belief in Allāh and His Messenger.\" He was asked: \"Then what?\" He replied: \"Jihād in the path of Allāh.\" He was asked: \"Then what?\" He replied: \"A Ḥaj Mabrūr.\" (Bukhārī, Muslim, Bayhaqī)",
