                englishText: "I heard the Messenger of Allāh (ﷺ) saying: 'Guarding the Islāmic borders for a single day in the path of Allāh is better than a thousand days in other places.'\" (Tirmidhī, Nasā'ī, Dārimī)",
                grade: "Hasan Sahih",
