                collection: "Muslim",
                commentary: `The Messenger of Allāh (ﷺ) gave the glad tidings of victory to the Ṣaḥābah, but reminded them that even when vast lands were conquered, they should never become complacent and abandon the knowledge of combat and warfare.`
