                englishText: "A man said: \"O Messenger of Allāh, grant me permission to travel.\" The Messenger of Allāh (ﷺ) replied: \"The travelling of my Ummah is jihād in the path of Allāh.\" (Abū Dāwūd, Bayhaqī, Ḥākim)",
