                englishText: "I witnessed that when the Messenger of Allāh (ﷺ) did not commence the battle in the beginning of the day, he would delay it until after midday, when the winds blew and the help (of Allāh) descended.\" (Abū Dāwūd, Aḥmad, Tirmidhī)",
