                englishText: "Abū Hurayrah (رضي الله عنه) and Jābir (رضي الله عنه) narrate that the Messenger of Allāh (ﷺ) said: \"War is deception.\" (Bukhārī, Muslim, Abū Dāwūd, Tirmidhī)",
