                englishText: "The Messenger of Allāh (ﷺ) said: \"The superiority of a scholar over a worshipper is like my superiority over the lowest among you.\" The Messenger of Allāh (ﷺ) then said: \"Allāh, His angels, the inhabitants of the heavens and the earth, even an ant in its hole and the fish, send special mercies upon the person who teaches people good.\" (Tirmidhī, Dārimī, Ṭabrānī)",
