                englishText: "The Messenger of Allāh (ﷺ) said: \"One who acquires knowledge by which the pleasure of Allāh is sought, in order to acquire worldly gains, will not experience the fragrance of Paradise on the day of Qiyāmah.\" (Abū Dāwūd, Ibn Mājah, Aḥmad)",
