                englishText: "The Messenger of Allāh (ﷺ) said: \"When a servant's child passes away, Allāh says to His angels: 'Have you taken the child of My servant?' They reply: 'Yes.' He then asks: 'Have you taken the fruit of his heart?' They reply: 'Yes.' He then asks: 'What did My servant say?' They reply: 'He praised You and said: To Allāh we belong and to Him is our return.' Allāh says: 'Build for My servant a house in Paradise and name it Bayt al-Ḥamd (the house of praise).'\" (Tirmidhī)",
