                englishText: "The Messenger of Allāh (ﷺ) said: \"May that person be humiliated who, when my name is mentioned in his presence, does not send salutations upon me.\" (Tirmidhī, Ḥākim, Ibn Ḥibbān)",
                grade: "Hasan",
