                englishText: "The Messenger of Allāh (ﷺ) said: \"No person sends greetings of peace upon me without Allāh returning my soul to me so that I may return the greeting to him.\" (Abū Dāwūd, Aḥmad, Bayhaqī)",
                grade: "Sahih",
