                englishText: "The Messenger of Allāh (ﷺ) said: \"There are two phrases which are light on the tongue, weighty in the scale, and most beloved to the Merciful (Allāh): 'Glory be to Allāh and praise be to Him. Glory be to Allāh, the Majestic.'\" (Bukhārī, Muslim, Tirmidhī, Ibn Mājah)",
