                englishText: "The Messenger of Allāh (ﷺ) said: \"None will bring anything on the day of Qiyāmah better than one who says in the morning and in the evening 100 times, 'Glory be to Allāh and praise be to Him,' except a person who says the same or more.\" (Muslim)",
