                englishText: "A man came to the Messenger of Allāh (ﷺ) and said: \"O Messenger of Allāh, how severely I was stung by a scorpion last night.\" He said: \"If you had said, 'I seek refuge with the perfect words of Allāh from the evil of what He has created,' it would not have harmed you.\" (Muslim, Aḥmad)",
