                englishText: "The Messenger of Allāh (ﷺ) said to me: 'Recite Qul huwallāhu aḥad (Sūrah al-Ikhlāṣ), and the Mu'awwadhatayn (Sūrah al-Falaq and Sūrah al-Nās) in the morning and evening three times. They will be sufficient for you from everything.'\" (Abū Dāwūd, Aḥmad)",
