                englishText: "The Messenger of Allāh (ﷺ) said: \"When any of you retires to his bed, he should dust his bed with the inside of his loin cloth because he does not know what might be on it. He should then say: 'In Your name, My Sustainer, I place my side (on the bed) and through Your name I raise it up. If You take away my soul, have mercy upon it. If You release it, protect it like You protect Your righteous servants.'\" (Bukhārī, Muslim, Aḥmad)",
                grade: "Sahih",
