                englishText: "When the Messenger of Allāh (ﷺ) retired to his bed, he said: 'All praise is due to Allāh who granted us food and drink, and who gave us sufficient and provided us with shelter. There are so many people who do not have sufficient and who have no shelter.'\" (Muslim)",
