                commentary: `This ḥadīth was mentioned previously. See ḥadīth 336. It is repeated here to highlight the severity of giving false testimony. It is a major sin because the harms of it are not confined to a single individual, but often have broad implications in society. The fact that it has been mentioned in the same breath as ascribing partners to Allāh and disobedience to parents illustrates its evil.`
