                englishText: "A young girl was once riding on a camel with some goods of people and the Messenger of Allāh (ﷺ) came into her sight. The mountains restricted them, so she said (to the camel): 'Move faster. O Allāh! Curse it.' The Messenger of Allāh (ﷺ) said: 'A camel that has been cursed may no longer travel with us.'\" (Muslim)",
