                englishText: "I was with the Messenger of Allāh (ﷺ) while Maymūnah (رضي الله عنها) was with him. Ibn Umm Maktūm (رضي الله عنه) approached, and this was after we had been commanded with ḥijāb. The Messenger of Allāh (ﷺ) said: 'Veil yourselves from him.' We said: 'O Messenger of Allāh! Is he not blind and therefore cannot see us and recognise us!?' The Messenger of Allāh (ﷺ) said: 'Are you two also blind? Can you not see him?'\" (Abū Dāwūd, Tirmidhī, Aḥmad)",
