                englishText: "The Messenger of Allāh (ﷺ) said: \"A man should not look at another man's private parts, nor a woman at another woman's private parts. A man should not lie next to another man while sharing the same sheet, nor should a woman lie next to another woman while sharing the same sheet.\" (Muslim, Abū Dāwūd, Ḥākim)",
