                englishText: "Ṣafiyyah bint Abī 'Ubayd relates from one of the wives of the Messenger of Allāh (ﷺ) that he said: \"One who goes to a diviner and asks him something, and then believes it, his ṣalāh will not be accepted for forty days.\" (Muslim)",
