                englishText: "I said: 'O Messenger of Allāh! I just recently left ignorance and Allāh brought Islām, but there are still some among us who go to fortune tellers.' He said: 'Do not go to them.' I said: 'There are some among us who take good and evil omens from the flight of birds.' He said: 'That is something which they experience in their hearts, so it should not prevent them (from their objective).' I said: 'There are those among us who practise geomancy.' He said: 'One of the Messengers used to practise geomancy, so one whose geomancy conforms with his (the Messenger's) geomancy, it is correct.'\" (Muslim)",
