                englishText: "The taking of omens was mentioned in the presence of the Messenger of Allāh (ﷺ). He said: 'The best omen is a good omen, but it should not deter a Muslim (from his objective). When any of you sees something that he dislikes, he should say: \"O Allāh! None but You brings good and none but You repels evil. There is no might and power except from You.\"' (Abū Dāwūd)",
