                englishText: "Abū al-Sha'thā' narrates: \"We were sitting with Abū Hurayrah (رضي الله عنه) in the masjid and the mu'adhdhin called out the adhān. A man stood up and walked out of the masjid. Abū Hurayrah (رضي الله عنه) watched him until he left the masjid. Abū Hurayrah (رضي الله عنه) then said: 'This person has disobeyed Abū al-Qāsim (ﷺ).'\" (Muslim)",
