                englishText: "The Messenger of Allāh (ﷺ) saw me wearing two yellow-coloured garments. He said: 'Did your mother order you to wear this?' I replied: 'Should I wash them?' He said: 'No, rather burn them.'\" Another narration has: \"These are the garments of the disbelievers, so do not wear them.\" (Muslim, Aḥmad)",
