                englishText: "The Messenger of Allāh (ﷺ) said: \"One who ascribes lineage to someone other than his own father while knowing that that person is not his father, then Paradise is unlawful for him.\" (Bukhārī, Muslim, Aḥmad, Ibn Mājah)",
