                englishText: "The Messenger of Allāh (ﷺ) said: \"O assembly of women! Give ṣadaqah and seek forgiveness in abundance because I have seen that you are the majority of the inmates of the Hell-fire.\" One of the women asked: \"Why are we the majority of the inmates of the Hell-fire?\" He replied: \"You curse a lot and you are ungrateful to your husbands. Despite the fact that I see you deficient in intellect and religion, you can overpower a man of intelligence.\" She asked: \"What is the deficiency in our intellect and religion?\" He said: \"The testimony of two women is equal to that of one man, and there are some days when you do not perform ṣalāh (due to menstruation).\" (Muslim, Aḥmad, Ibn Mājah)",
