                commentary: `Some may ask why they will have fragrant burners when their bodily fragrance will be one of musk. The answer is that the fragrances of Paradise will be merely for pleasure and enjoyment and not due to necessity. Men in Paradise will all be handsome in form and features. None will be excessively tall, short, fat or thin. They will be around 30 meters in length because Paradise will similarly be huge in size. Each man will have a minimum of two wives excluding the damsels. The reference to their shin bones being seen through the flesh is to indicate their exceptional purity and beauty. Their hearts will be united and free from hatred because they will be purified of every distasteful quality before entering Paradise.`
